{% extends "BookBundle::layout.html.twig" %}
{% block body %}
    <h1>Want to use the ReviewStar's external API?</h1>
    <h2>Use the required OAuth2 request headers in your client side app</h2>
    <h5>Remember, you need to be registered to gain access to the external API with your credentials</h5>
    <p><b>With secret key:</b> {{ client.getSecret() }}</p>
    <p><b>With id:</b> 1_{{ client.randomId() }}</p>
    <p>For your body, enter the above details as client_secret and client_id respectively. With a grant_type of password, and username and password representing your username and password on this site.
    Put these details in your request body, making a POST to /oauth/v2/token.</p>
{% endblock %}